AngloGold Says Worker Dies, Four Injusted in Accident at Mponeng Mine

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-05-27T14:22:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-27/anglogold-says-worker-dies-four-injusted-in-accident-at-mponeng-mine.html
AngloGold Ashanti Ltd. (ANG)  said a worker
died at its Mponeng mine in  South Africa  and four others were
injured today after an earth tremor caused an accident.  AngloGold commented in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  